ing: 1 1/2 cups KRAFT Shredded Triple Cheddar Cheese with a TOUCH OF PHILADELPHIA
des: "Fig with prosciutto--a classic flavor pairing--with walnuts, shredded Cheddar cheese, and fresh rosemary make an easy yet elegant appetizer on baguette rounds."
ins:
Heat broiler.
Place bread slices in single layer on baking sheet; spread with jam.
Top with remaining ingredients.
Broil, 4 inches from heat, 3 min. or until cheese is melted.
